mic changes associated with globalization.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aLAW / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150362575440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503625754423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503625754/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles